{"tid":1351624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"727慎防多重戰線，人多先安全","createTime":"2019-07-22T15:56:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T23:19:40.000Z","uid":132362,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6edc78a3b13204e088f75ba8bc43f97d37e814ff","tid":1351624,"uid":132362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:56:42.000Z","msg":"仆你地個街，係咁叫人唔好去光復元朗<br />\n明明琴晚30000人話要燒村<br />\n而家又和理非留屋企、女人留屋企<br />\n想點撚樣<br />\n<br />\n仲有傻西叫有經驗既義士入村，其他人去第二到玩<br />\n係唔係想義士死曬？<br />\n<br />\n仲叫人分兩條線打，721教訓就係多重戰線既話<br />\n有一邊既努力係白費<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人多就安全<br />\n人少死硬<br />\n到而家都唔明？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一係就唔入元朗，一係就要幾十萬人，唔係死緊"},{"pid":"73f5c9a5b1eb80c6a482c8f87184fda6e8b8cf25","tid":1351624,"uid":132362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:58:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1829cfafdf9392e5b616949860fe9bbb6d484545","tid":1351624,"uid":118888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:59:54.000Z","msg":"人多先安全"},{"pid":"956dc7cc72136fc18b581d58c8b1743b103ef0f2","tid":1351624,"uid":132362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:00:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"41202031659daf4678e63bbd85e9980854b81209","tid":1351624,"uid":132362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:03:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f736924fb9aa212ba461560986b096e3d2331e6","tid":1351624,"uid":263521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:09:49.000Z","msg":"人多先安全<br />\n人多就勢眾<br />\n到時一人一腳佢都邊殘廢<br />\n到時先準備繩<br />\n將佢地五花大綁<br />\n遊街示眾😤😤"},{"pid":"7c1a65477e12ff98a75f886dc522dc16a78266a6","tid":1351624,"uid":132362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16